room_title: Escape room "Captainâ€™s Quarters" by The Room Upstairs in Chicago
room_description: Ahoy ye landlubbers! Back in the 1600s that scurvy pirate, Captain Mayhem, plundered and looted everybody and everything.  Nothing was left untouched by his greed, including you and your mateys.   He stole your treasure!  Now, you have snuck onto his ship.  Will you be able to solve the riddles, clues, and puzzles in order to find and reclaim your treasure before he returns and makes you walk the plank?
